{"type": "article", "id": 24451, "title": "像扇叶一样的隔热工具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-25T07:00:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607103852zT3EbxOKyFYnQGat.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个隔热的小工具，绿色部分是硅材料。将它平摊后呈现出十字型，可以承担温度很高的铁锅以及多种型号。沿着中间的圆环拉起来后，四个扇叶则会因金属的重力而朝下，像一个三脚架，有方便悬挂的特征，简单而实用。<a href=\"http://www.hktdc.com/suppliers-products/Heli-Trivet-Heat-Resistant-Mat/en/1X002R5M/2829998/\">点击这里尝试购买。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103851RTH1eL5lSZXj4zrf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.37142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607103851VPw7ebACxEQpl36X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.36857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}